title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Aug 31 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Aug 31 2022
description:
Clay & Buck dissect Joe Biden's speech in Wilkes Barre, Pennsylvania yesterday. Clay and Buck break down the Pennsylvania Senate race and Democrat Nominee John Fetterman's Reluctance to debate Dr. Ox. Clay calls for Fetterman to drop out of the race. Senator Marco Rubio is the guest. He explains why his Democrat opponent, Rep. Val Demings is a do-nothing candidate and surprises Clay & Buck with his pick for best Eddie Murphy movie. Kari Lake breaks down the Arizona gubernatorial race.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
